msgstr "**2. 启动容器**"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:37
msgid "The ``start.sh`` script automatically performs the following:"
msgstr "``start.sh`` 脚本会自动执行以下操作："

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:39
msgid "Detects the NVIDIA driver version"
msgstr "检测 NVIDIA 驱动版本"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:40
msgid "Mounts GPU devices and libraries"
msgstr "挂载 GPU 设备与库文件"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:41
msgid "Sets the required environment variables"
msgstr "设置所需环境变量"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:42
msgid "Mounts data and output directories"
msgstr "挂载数据与输出目录"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:44
msgid "**3. Run inference**"
msgstr "**3. 执行推理**"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:46
msgid "Execute inside the container:"
msgstr "在容器内执行："

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:62
msgid ""
"After exiting the container, output files are located in the ``output/`` "
"directory on the host."
msgstr "退出容器后，输出文件位于宿主机的 ``output/`` 目录。"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:65
msgid "Important Notes"
msgstr "重要说明"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:67
msgid "**CUDA only**"
msgstr "**仅支持 CUDA**"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:69
msgid ""
"The decryption logic for the encrypted models is compiled into the C++ "
"engine and can only be initialized on a CUDA device. Using ``--device cpu`` "
"will cause silent model initialization failure."
msgstr ""
"加密模型的解密逻辑已编译进 C++ 引擎，且仅可在 CUDA 设备上初始化。使用 ``--device cpu`` 会导致模型初始化静默失败。"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:71
msgid "**GPU mounting**"
msgstr "**GPU 挂载**"

#: ../../platform/deployment.rst:73
msgid ""
"On some systems (e.g., Rocky Linux 9.2), CDI mode (``--device "
"nvidia.com/gpu=all``) may not work correctly. ``start.sh`` resolves this by "
"manually mounting ``/dev/nvidia*`` devices and the host NVIDIA libraries."
msgstr ""
"在部分系统（如 Rocky Linux 9.2）中，CDI 模式（``--device "
"nvidia.com/gpu=all``）可能无法正常工作。``start.sh`` 通过手动挂载 ``/dev/nvidia*`` 设备及宿主机 "
"NVIDIA 库文件解决该问题。"

